A '''sialoblastoma''' is a low-grade [[salivary gland]] [[neoplasm]] that recapitulates primitive salivary gland [[Primordium|anlage]]. It has previously been referred to as ''congenital basal cell adenoma'', ''embryoma'', or ''basaloid adenocarcinoma''.
It is an extremely rare tumor, with less than 100 cases reported worldwide.<ref name="Som">{{cite journal
